{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "家康（夏日Ver.） 第2话 学习当地智慧",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "呼……这下你已经\\n把这附近的设施\\n都看了一圈了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "嗯，多亏了你带路，\\n谢谢你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "没事啦，你还在海之家\\n请我大吃特吃了呢，\\n虽然你吃得比我还多。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "这家伙是个甜党，\\n看见国外的新奇甜品\\n就高兴得要命。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "哈哈……很美味哦。\\n不过最值得一提的\\n还是这片海滩的治安。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "吃甜品的时候也没有\\n看到什么惹眼的骚动。\\n这一带没有魔兽出没吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "有倒是有，\\n可很少会给海滩造成骚乱，\\n因为有自卫团和救援队在。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "自卫团和……救援队？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "就是盯着海里有没有人溺水，\\n有的话就前去营救的那些人。\\n另外他们还会帮忙消灭海里的魔兽。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "啊，水上安全监督员啊。原来如此。\\n监督员也接受过突发情况的训练，\\n还和陆上的警卫联手……很周全呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "没错！所以魔兽跑到海滩上\\n这种事几年都不见得有一次，\\n大家才能放心地玩！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "哦，这样啊，\\n不过对于我这战龙来说\\n好像缺了点什么——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "游客",
            "context": "呀、呀啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "喂，怎么回事！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120233_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "螃蟹——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120068_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "救生员",
            "context": "唔！这家伙不好对付！\\n要抑制不住了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "不好，是大型魔兽！\\n已经冲破了警卫员的包围，\\n朝着这边来了……赛塔，快逃！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "诶？诶？魔兽？为什么……\\n明明很少会有魔兽\\n跑到海滩这边来的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120233_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "螃蟹！螃蟹～",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "呀！啊、啊、啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "休想得逞！\\n看招，辰花连刃流！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "唔，火势太猛了！\\n这样剑伤不到它……摩利支天！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "看我的吧！把你打进海里\\n灭个火！嘿呀！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120233_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "螃蟹！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "漂亮！只要它稍微老实点，\\n我就有办法……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120233_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "螃蟹……螃蟹！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "啊……魔、魔兽又爬起来\\n跑回来了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "啧，没能干掉它，\\n竟然还能动弹啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "是啊，虽说是缓兵之计，\\n但还是争取到了时间……\\n赛塔，你没事吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "好、好厉害！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "赛塔？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "家康哥哥，你好厉害呀！\\n你刚才的剑法是怎么回事！？\\n唰唰几下我都没看清！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "说实话，我还以为你不谙世事，\\n没想到你是身手高强的剑士，\\n我对你刮目相看了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "哈哈哈……\\n承蒙夸奖。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "但别高兴得太早。\\n魔兽用不了多久\\n就会回到这片海滩上。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "不想办法解决它的火焰防守，\\n就没法从根本上解决问题。\\n要怎么办才好……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "的确如此。唔～火焰……\\n解决火焰……唔……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "啊！我想到了一个主意！\\n家康哥哥，我现在说的\\n这个方案，你能帮个忙吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "我有个好主意！\\n要是有你这么厉害的高手\\n帮我的忙，也许就能成功！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120233_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "螃蟹！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "好……魔兽回来了！\\n家康哥哥，我们按计划行事，\\n把它往对面的岛那边赶！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "收到。辰花连刃流，看招！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120233_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "螃蟹！？螃蟹！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "好，上钩了，就这么牵住！\\n小子，不想受伤的话\\n可别跑到我前头去啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "嗯！家康哥哥，\\n再往右，往右边！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "好！压制住它……哈啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120233_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "螃蟹！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "趁现在！家康哥哥上啊！\\n把它扔到岛附近去！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "交给我吧！\\n奥义，夜樱八连斩！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120233_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "螃蟹！？螃蟹螃蟹……螃蟹！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "好！成功了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "真叫人吃惊……\\n那家伙一下就沉底没声了。\\n到底有什么玄机？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "嘿嘿，那座岛周围是禁止游泳的\\n危险区域。据说有连游泳高手\\n也会淹死的夺命急流……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "不管多壮实的魔兽\\n掉进那里也得完蛋。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "哈，原来如此，所以只要\\n靠家康的力量把它赶过去就好。\\n你小子挺厉害嘛！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "嘿嘿，还好啦。说到底，\\n魔兽也无法战胜大海的力量。\\n总之，这件事算是告一段落……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120233_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "螃蟹！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "不、不会吧！？竟然还活着……\\n哇啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "奥义，夜樱十六连斩！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120233_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "嘎啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "呼……千钧一发。\\n赛塔，你站得起来吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "……\\n已经……打倒魔兽了吗！？\\n家康哥哥，你果然厉害啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "它被冲进海口的夺命急流里，\\n周身的火焰消失了，\\n所以我的剑才能奏效。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "这不是我的功劳，\\n而是靠你的作战方案。\\n这都是多亏了当地传承的智慧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "当地的、智慧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "没错，最了解一方水土的\\n果然还是那一方的人——\\n这次的经历让我领悟到了这一点。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "回到祖国之后，\\n也许应该积极录用\\n本地人才当海边警卫。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "噢，这主意不错。本地人\\n也许还熟悉近路之类的呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "是啊，呵呵。多亏了赛塔，\\n视察进展顺利，令人欣喜。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "赛塔，再次感谢你引路，\\n还有……如果你愿意，\\n之后也都拜托你了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120073_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛塔",
            "context": "嗯！包在我身上！\\n明天我们也多去转一转吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}